snippet.title: Christina Ricci Says 'Matrix' Co-Star Keanu Reeves Was 'Cool', Talks 'Yellowjackets' S1 | EXTENDED
snippet.description:
Christina Ricci is bringing a little anarchy and punk to her new role in "Yellowjackets" the part survival story, part psychological horror story about a girls soccer team who survive a plane crash. The actress also shares what she can about working with Keanu Reeves on "The Matrix Resurrections". 

#ChristinaRicci #KeanuReeves #TheMatrixResurrections
